@startuml 智慧停车平台-用例图
' ============================================
' 用例图：AI-driven 城市智慧停车管理与诱导系统
' 作者：19组 PM 丁梓钊
' 版本：V1.0
' ============================================

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "私家车主" as Driver
actor "停车场管理员" as Admin
actor "系统" as System <<system>>

rectangle "智慧停车管理平台" {
  
  ' --- 车主用例 ---
  usecase (UC-01 用户注册与登录) as UC01
  usecase (UC-02 浏览停车场信息) as UC02
  usecase (UC-03 车位实时查询) as UC03
  usecase (UC-04 车位在线预约) as UC04
  usecase (UC-05 停车计费与支付) as UC05
  usecase (UC-06 查看停车记录) as UC06
  usecase (UC-07 反向寻车) as UC07
  
  ' --- 管理员用例 ---
  usecase (UC-08 管理停车场信息) as UC08
  usecase (UC-09 查看运营数据) as UC09
  usecase (UC-10 查看数据看板) as UC10
  
  ' --- 包含关系 ---
  UC03 ..> UC02 : <<include>>
  UC04 ..> UC03 : <<include>>
  UC05 ..> (系统计算费用) : <<include>>
  UC06 ..> UC01 : <<include>>
  UC07 ..> UC01 : <<include>>
  UC09 ..> UC08 : <<include>>
  UC10 ..> UC09 : <<include>>
}

' --- 角色关联 ---
Driver --> UC01
Driver --> UC02
Driver --> UC03
Driver --> UC04
Driver --> UC05
Driver --> UC06
Driver --> UC07

Admin --> UC01
Admin --> UC08
Admin --> UC09
Admin --> UC10

note right of UC04
  预约锁定15分钟
  超时自动释放
end note

note bottom of UC05
  模拟支付流程
  不接入真实支付
end note

@enduml
